    <!-- EXECUTIVE SUMMARY -->
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-100">
            <h2 id="executive-summary" style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--header-font);">Executive Summary</h2>
            
            <div style="background: var(--info-color, #d1ecf1); border-left: 4px solid var(--info-border, #17a2b8); padding: var(--spacing-medium); margin: var(--spacing-medium) 0; border-radius: 3px;">
                <p style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font); margin: 0;">
                    <strong>Phase 2 Objective:</strong> Implement the backend services and integrations required for the AI Chat system to function end-to-end. This phase covers document indexing, LLM model integration, chat request handling, and role-based access control enforcement.
                </p>
            </div>

            <h3 style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--header-font);">Phase 2 Deliverables</h3>
            <ul style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font);">
                <li><strong>DocumentationIndexer Service:</strong> Scans and indexes .tt documentation files with FULLTEXT search capability</li>
                <li><strong>Ollama Integration:</strong> Local LLM support for all users (free, privacy-focused)</li>
                <li><strong>XAI Integration:</strong> Cloud-based LLM for developers/admins (advanced models)</li>
                <li><strong>Chat Controller:</strong> HTTP endpoint handling chat requests, model selection, and response generation</li>
                <li><strong>Role-Based Access Control:</strong> Enforce documentation and feature access based on user roles</li>
            </ul>

            <p style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font); margin-top: var(--spacing-large);"><strong>Estimated Total Effort:</strong> 26-35 hours of development</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- PHASE 2 OVERVIEW -->
