        <div class="col-100">
            <h2 id="phase-2-overview" style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--header-font);">Phase 2 Overview</h2>

            <div style="background: var(--warning-color, #fff3cd); border-left: 4px solid var(--warning-border, #ffc107); padding: var(--spacing-medium); margin: var(--spacing-medium) 0; border-radius: 3px;">
                <p style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font); margin: 0;">
                    <strong>Dependency:</strong> Phase 2 builds on Phase 1 (Database & Model Layer). All database tables, Result classes, and startup automation from Phase 1 must be complete before starting Phase 2.
                </p>
            </div>

