    <!-- RELATED DOCUMENTATION -->
    <div class="row" style="margin-top: var(--spacing-large);">
        <div class="col-100">
            <h2 id="related-documentation" style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--header-font);">Phase 2 Related Documentation</h2>

            <div style="background: var(--info-color, #d1ecf1); border-left: 4px solid var(--info-border, #17a2b8); padding: var(--spacing-medium); margin: var(--spacing-medium) 0; border-radius: 3px;">
                <p style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font); margin: 0;">
                    The following documents provide detailed guidance on Phase 2 implementation areas. These should be reviewed before starting backend service development.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div style="margin: var(--spacing-large) 0;">
                <h3 style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--header-font);">📚 Essential Phase 2 Guides</h3>
                <ul style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font);">
                    <li><strong><a href="/Documentation/DBSchemaManager_Usage_Guide" style="color: var(--link-color);">DBSchemaManager Usage Guide</a></strong> - Comprehensive guide to using DBSchemaManager for schema creation and management. Essential reading before implementing DocumentationIndexer.</li>
                    <li><strong><a href="/Documentation/AI_Chat_Schema_Documentation" style="color: var(--link-color);">AI Chat Schema Documentation</a></strong> - Complete documentation of all AI Chat database tables, columns, relationships, and indexing strategies.</li>
