                <p style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font); margin: 0;">
                    Phase 2 is successfully completed when all 5 components are implemented, tested, and integrated.
                </p>
            </div>

            <h3 style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--header-font);">Completion Checklist</h3>
            <ul style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font);">
                <li>☐ <strong>Documentation Indexer:</strong> Automatically indexes all .tt files on startup and periodically</li>
                <li>☐ <strong>Ollama Integration:</strong> Local models available and responding to queries</li>
                <li>☐ <strong>XAI Integration:</strong> Cloud models available to authorized users</li>
                <li>☐ <strong>Chat Controller:</strong> Accepts and responds to chat requests with citations</li>
                <li>☐ <strong>Role-Based Access:</strong> Users only see/access appropriate resources</li>
                <li>☐ <strong>Conversation Logging:</strong> All chats stored in database with metadata</li>
                <li>☐ <strong>Error Handling:</strong> Graceful fallback when services unavailable</li>
                <li>☐ <strong>Unit Tests:</strong> &gt;80% code coverage for all components</li>
                <li>☐ <strong>Documentation:</strong> API documentation completed</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- FOOTER -->
